net.siliconcode.parsers.csharp

Class CSharp5BaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.siliconcode.parsers.csharp.CSharp5BaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CSharp5Listener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class CSharp5BaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements CSharp5Listener
    This class provides an empty implementation of CSharp5Listener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
